				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Which template you'd like to change? An error message that the posting is rejected? If yes, then:
<br />

<br />
* the error box layout is defined by phpBB itself, in the file &quot;templates/subSilver/error_body.tpl&quot;,
<br />
* the text of the message is defined by bbAntiSpam, in the language file &quot;language/lang_english/lang_bbas.php&quot;,
<br />
* list of the URLs is constructed in the bbAntiSpam code, in the file &quot;includes/functions_bbas.php&quot;.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
